{"tid":1667140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應叫印度協會前主席小心說話 鄭泳舜表示 無其他意思","createTime":"2019-10-21T09:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T09:58:25.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12366ac393294196d2243468212454d2b0d343bb","tid":1667140,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:49:51.000Z","msg":"警方水炮車昨日（20 日）向尖沙嘴清真寺正門噴射藍色水，被射中的印度協會前主席毛漢褚簡寧（Mohan Chugani）向傳媒透露，民建聯立法會議員鄭泳舜昨晚曾到他家探望，並叫他對傳媒說話時要小心一點。鄭泳舜書面回覆傳媒查詢時表示，他的言論並無其他用意。<br />\n<br />\n鄭泳舜書面回覆香港電台查詢時表示，昨日知悉情況後聯同黨友前往探望毛漢褚簡寧 ，慰問傷勢及了解可提供甚麼協助&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%AB%E5%8D%B0%E5%8D%94%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%AF%9B%E6%BC%A2-%E8%AA%AA%E8%A9%B1%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E9%BB%9E-%E9%84%AD%E6%B3%B3%E8%88%9C-%E7%84%A1%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%94%A8%E6%84%8F/#.Xa18Ix6pDWI.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25BC%25A2-%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E8%2588%259C-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2585%25B6%25E4%25BB%2596%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2584%258F%2F%23.Xa18Ix6pDWI.facebook&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=c108b58c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25BC%25A2-%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E8%2588%259C-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2585%25B6%25E4%25BB%2596%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2584%258F%2F%23.Xa18Ix6pDWI.facebook&h=17dd8a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%AB%E5%8D%B0%E5%8D%94%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%AF%9B%E6%BC%A2-%E8%AA%AA%E8%A9%B1%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E9%BB%9E-%E9%84%AD%E6%B3%B3%E8%88%9C-%E7%84%A1%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%94%A8%E6%84%8F/#.Xa18Ix6pDWI.facebook</a>"},{"pid":"2c690a8df6dad35494c0d39d3cf82156b26236f5","tid":1667140,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:52:04.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"f83dc14828fa8b9555770ab2a01b46d05eb8caca","tid":1667140,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8b8470f778fcf93ff09d7daa66d9c4b8cc143b","tid":1667140,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:58:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位宣傳一個idea。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1</a><br />\n[文宣升級] 郵差叔叔送信純熟將文宣迅速送出!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H03stW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H03stW.png&h=37a4782b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}